                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Does it already? See &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/browse/ROO-1368&quot; title=&quot;Document that chained persistence in RequestFactory requires typical single EntityManager per request set up&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;ROO-1368&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;ROO-1368&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for why.&lt;/p&gt;

